{"tid":1215272,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今個星期尾需要有大型集會或者遊行重新向香港政府宣戰","createTime":"2019-06-13T06:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:54:00.000Z","uid":87571,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e648c881ec0e00121ab39dab53fdfe4e72795904","tid":1215272,"uid":87571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:36:43.000Z","msg":"一定要重新再召集上次遊行嘅一百萬人出嚟。要好清晰咁話俾香港政府同全世界聽民意係喺我哋呢邊。<br />\n<br />\n重新集氣<br />\n一方面可以話俾政府聽我哋未放棄<br />\n二來可以持續上到外國新聞頭版爭取關注<br />\n<br />\n而家美國國會係日內就會重新討論香港人權同民主法例，呢條法例好大影響有機會令香港政府或者中央撤回逃犯條例。如果我哋冇幾十萬人再出嚟，人哋可能會覺得呢件事唔再重要冇心討論。"},{"pid":"d1fcaef09dadd511f4399ec87ffa57cd0265d4c8","tid":1215272,"uid":87571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5379da2160de1afcfedd1ce62c663e47ee2fbe93","tid":1215272,"uid":87571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:41:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9f5a724f21c9c76a449e8f18ced0dfd36560bac","tid":1215272,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:46:56.000Z","msg":"推 民陣攪唔今 <br />\n今次一定要和平"},{"pid":"6398cbdf718e3768aad2ad8deef39c95825ee7c9","tid":1215272,"uid":87571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:47:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0cee620e0bae661c470afd6ab0425e3dc1e253d","tid":1215272,"uid":87571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:50:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0649e577075d3bfa037c71b9f1081dde15967791","tid":1215272,"uid":87571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:54:00.000Z","msg":"推"}]}